Khan%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20August%201%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20the%20diplomatic%20cable%20saga%20-%20a%20cypher%20what%20the%20former%20premier%20claimed%20contains%20details%20of%20a%20threat%20made%20by%20the%20US%20against%20his%20government%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhan%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20office%20in%20April%20last%20year.%C2%A0In%20a%20public%20gathering%20on%20March%202022%2C%20Khan%20waived%20a%20letter%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20evidence%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinternational%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20backed%20by%20the%20US%20to%20topple%20his%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20earlier%20also%2C%20the%20FIA%20has%20grilled%20the%20ex-prime%20minister%20for%20nearly%20two%20hours%20and%20recorded%20his%20statement%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fresh%20notice%2C%20the%20investigation%20agency%20asked%20Khan%20to%20appear%20before%20its%20joint%20investigation%20team%20at%20noon%20on%20August%201%20with%20all%20the%20relevant%20documents%2C%20according%20to%20Geo%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20federal%20agency%20interrogated%20PTI%20Vice%20Chairman%20Shah%20Mahmood%20Qureshi%20for%20nearly%20two%20hours%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20ongoing%20probe%20into%20the%20controversial%20US%20cypher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cypher%20drama%20took%20a%20new%20turn%20last%20week%20when%20PTI%20Chief's%20aide%20Azam%20Khan%20recorded%20a%20statement%20before%20the%20magistrate%20and%20revealed%20that%20the%20then-prime%20minister%20(Imran%20Khan)%2C%20in%202022%2C%20used%20a%20diplomatic%20cypher%20sent%20by%20Pakistan's%20envoy%20to%20Washington%20to%20concoct%20a%20narrative%20against%20the%20establishment%20and%20the%20Opposition%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzam%2C%20who%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bmissing%26quot%3B%20since%20last%20month%2C%20recorded%20his%20statement%20under%20CrPC%20164%20before%20a%20magistrate%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20statement%20on%20the%20cypher%20case%2C%20the%20former%20PM%20said%20that%20he%20will%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20matter%20until%20the%20complete%20information%20comes%20out.%20He%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20known%20yet%20in%20what%20circumstances%20Azam%20Khan%20made%20these%20statements%2C%20according%20to%20ARY%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Interior%20Minister%20Rana%20Sanaullah%20asserted%20that%20the%20confessional%20statement%20of%20ex-principal%20secretary%20Azam%20Khan%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98charge%20sheet'%20against%20PTI%20chief%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20the%20latter%20should%20be%20punished%20for%20anti-state%20%E2%80%98cypher%20drama'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20chairman%20%5BImran%20Khan%5D%20tarnished%20the%20reputation%20of%20state%20institutions%20through%20cypher%20conspiracy.%20He%20should%20be%20punished%20for%20staging%20the%20drama%2C%E2%80%9D%20Geo%20News%20quoted%20Sanaullah%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20the%20cypher%20conspiracy%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20May%209%20incident%20was%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20same%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPTI%20chairman%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20this%20crime.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20national%20interest%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20interior%20minister%20added%2C%20as%20per%20Geo%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690422240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhkla3vog_imran-khanpakistan_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-investigation-agency-summons-imran-khan-yet-again-in-cypher-case-4243736%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Federal%20Investigation%20Agency%20summoned%20Pakistan%20Tehreek