20other%20big%20US%20tech%20companies%2C%20Meta's%20share%20price%20has%20had%20a%20stellar%202023%20that%20Zuckerberg%20in%20January%20said%20would%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Byear%20of%20efficiency%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20two%20straight%20quarters%20of%20positive%20revenue%20growth%20and%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20double-digit%20revenue%20growth%20since%20late%202021%2C%20Meta's%20year%20of%20efficiency%20is%20off%20to%20a%20strong%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Insider%20Intelligence%20analyst%20Debra%20Aho%20Williamson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20to%20feel%20good%20about%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Meta%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Williamson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20shares%20were%20up%20more%20than%20seven%20percent%20%24320.32%20in%20after-market%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20earnings%20release%2C%20the%20company%20said%20that%20the%20number%20of%20ads%20on%20its%20various%20applications%20rose%20by%2034%20percent%20year-on-year%20in%20the%20second%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20noted%20the%20greater%20interest%20from%20advertisers%20in%20Reels%2C%20the%20video%20format%20copied%20from%20TikTok%2C%20and%20a%20less%20gloomy%20economic%20context%20conducive%20to%20marketing%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bgood%20progress%26quot%3B%20in%20bringing%20in%20money%20from%20Reels%2C%20with%20the%20video%20snippets%20played%20more%20than%20200%20billion%20times%20daily%20across%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20Zuckerberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVR%20costs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta's%20vow%20of%20austerity%20on%20spending%20brought%20an%20unprecedented%20round%20of%20cost-cutting%20that%20has%20seen%20the%20company%20lay%20off%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20workers%20since%20last%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20it%20had%2071%2C469%20employees%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20a%20decrease%20of%2014%20per%20cent%20from%20the%20same%20time%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20faced%20criticism%20over%20its%20gamble%20on%20the%20metaverse%2C%20the%20world%20of%20virtual%20reality%20that%20Meta%20believes%20will%20be%20the%20next%20frontier%20online%20and%20led%20it%20to%20change%20its%20name%20from%20Facebook%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20to%20date%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20bad%20bet%20with%20customers%20so%20far%20unenthused%20by%20the%20technology%2C%20even%20though%20Apple%20will%20enter%20the%20space%20sometime%20next%20year%20with%20the%20release%20of%20its%20expensive%20VisionPro%20headset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20referred%20to%20the%20lacklustre%20rate%20at%20which%20people%20are%20embracing%20the%20metaverse%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20sobering%20signal%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20remained%20confident%20it%20is%20a%20computing%20platform%20of%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20metaverse%20and%20AI%20remain%20priorities%20at%20Meta%2C%20according%20to%20Zuckerberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20said%20in%20the%20earnings%20report%20that%20it%20expects%20its%20operating%20losses%20at%20the%20unit%20responsible%20for%20VR%20to%20%26quot%3Bincrease%20meaningfully%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20year%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20jumped%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20chaos%20at%20Twitter%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20renamed%20to%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%20Meta%20rushed%20out%20the%20release%20of%20Threads%2C%20a%20text-only%20app%20that%20saw%20more%20than%20100%20million%20downloads%20in%20just%20days%2C%20though%20the%20users'%20longterm%20interest%20remains%20unproven.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20unprecedented%20growth%20out%20of%20the%20gate%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20we're%20seeing%20more%20people%20coming%20back%20daily%20than%20I'd%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20said%20of%20Threads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we're%20focused%20on%20retention%20and%20improving%20the%20basics%3B%20I'm%20really%20happy%20with%20the%20path%20that%20we're%20on%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20AI%2C%20Zuckerberg%20has%20chosen%20a%20different%20track%20than%20Microsoft%20and%20its%20partnership%20with%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeta%20instead%20has%20endorsed%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Bopen%20source%26quot%3B%20approach%20and%20made%20its%20Llama%20generative%20AI%20technology%20available%20to%20researchers%20and%20companies%20to%20adapt%20to%20their%20own%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20keen%20to%20see%20how%20Meta%20expands%20use%20of%20generative%20AI%20in%20its%20products%2C%20questions%20on%20the%20earnings%20call%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20indicated%20in%20a%20recent%20podcast%20that%20his%20company%20is%20working%20on%20an%20AI%20platform%20that%20would%20allow%20creators%20and%20advertisers%20to%20more%20efficiently%20work%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690421940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F2vqg2c0g_meta_625x300_23_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffacebook-parent-metas-earnings-beats-market-expectations-as-ads-revive-4243769%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Facebook%20parent%20Meta%20on%20Wednesday%20beat%20market%20expectations%20for%20quarterly%20earnings%2C%20powered%20by%20a%20reviving%20digital%20ad%20business.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffacebook-parent-metas-earnings-beats-market-expectations-as-ads-revive-4243769%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffacebook-parent-metas-earnings-beats-market-expectations-as-ads-revive-4243769%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22amp