C%22%3EWe%20are%20not%20alone%20--%20and%20American%20authorities%20are%20covering%20up%20the%20evidence%2C%20a%20former%20US%20intelligence%20officer%20told%20a%20congressional%20committee%20on%20Wednesday.%20David%20Grusch%20testified%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%26quot%3B%20believes%20the%20government%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20unidentified%20anomalous%20phenomena%2C%20or%20UAPs%20--%20which%20has%20replaced%20the%20term%20UFO%20in%20official%20parlance%20--%20as%20well%20as%20remains%20of%20their%20non-human%20operators.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fex-intel-officer-says-us-hiding-info-on-alien-craft%2Farticleshow%2F102153542.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fex-intel-officer-says-us-hiding-info-on-alien-craft%2Famp_articleshow%2F102153542.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fex-intel-officer-says-us-hiding-info-on-alien-craft%2Famp_articleshow%2F102153542.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Much%20Data%20Village%20and%20Ward%20Volunteers%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Collect%20From%20Voters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26172707%2FRI-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20and%20ward%20volunteer%20system%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20launched%20by%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20(YSRCP)%20government%20in%202019%2C%20has%20come%20under%20attack%20from%20opposition%20parties%2C%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20and%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%20chief%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20has%20alleged%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20that%20the%20volunteers%20(whose%20job%20is%20to%20provide%20last-mile%20governance%20and%20access%20to%20welfare%20schemes)%20are%20being%20used%20by%20the%20YSRCP%20to%20also%20conduct%20activities%20that%20benefit%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Jana%20Sena%20chief%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20household%20level%20data%20of%20citizens%20collected%20by%20the%20volunteers%2C%20particularly%20that%20of%20welfare%20scheme%20beneficiaries%2C%20is%20being%20misused%2C%20and%20raised%20concerns%20of%20data%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20cautioned%20people%20about%20sharing%20personal%20information%20with%20volunteers%2C%20while%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20declared%20that%20his%20party%20would%20move%20court%20against%20the%20volunteer%20system%20to%20protect%20personal%20data%20and%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVolunteers%20are%20entering%20homes%20and%20collecting%20people%E2%80%99s%20personal%20information%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20providing%20various%20benefits.%20They%20are%20even%20asking%20women%20if%20they%20suspect%20their%20husbands%20are%20having%20extramarital%20affairs.%20They%20are%20asking%20men%20what%20the%20women%20in%20their%20families%20are%20doing%20outside%20the%20home%E2%80%A6%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20this%20wrong%3F%20Privacy%20%5Bis%20important%5D%E2%80%A6%20Why%20do%20they%20need%20our%20personal%20information%3F%E2%80%9D%20Naidu%20asked%20on%20Friday%2C%20July%2014%2C%20while%20flagging%20off%20a%20procession%20focused%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20at%20the%20TDP%20headquarters%20in%20Mangalagiri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20unclear%20what%20kind%20of%20data%20inputs%20Naidu%20was%20talking%20about.%20However%2C%20information%20related%20to%20individuals%E2%80%99%20sex%20and%20marital%20lives%20including%20number%20of%20sex%20partners%2C%20instances%20of%20polygamy%2C%20domestic%20violence%20and%20attitudes%20towards%20contraception%2C%20etc.%20are%20gathered%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20village%20and%20ward%20volunteers%20are%20not%20involved%20in%20these%20surveys%2C%20as%20part%20of%20an%20education%20survey%2C%20volunteers%20were%20able%20to%20gather%20details%20of%20individuals%E2%80%99%20marital%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fin-andhra-jaganmohan-reddy-ysrcp-volunteers-privacy-voters-tech%5C%22%3EIn%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Government%20Volunteers%20Are%20Mapping%20Every%20Voter%20Household%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20actor-politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20made%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fandhra-govt-initiates-legal-action-against-pawan-kalyan-over-human-trafficking-allegations%5C%22%3Esensational%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20volunteers%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20were%20surveilling%20residents%20and%20targeting%20women%20living%20alone%2C%20to%20hand%20them%20over%20to%20%E2%80%9Canti-social%20forces%E2%80%9D%20who%20were%20kidnapping%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20has%20failed%20to%20furnish%20evidence%20to%20back%20these%20alarmist%20claims%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20figures%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fap-women-s-commission-seeks-proof-pawan-kalyan-s-claims-human-trafficking-179557%5C%22%3Ethat%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20cited%20for%20untraced%20missing%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20too%20are%20way%20above%20the%20official%20numbers%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20While%20he%20claimed%20that%2017%2C000%20to%2018%2C000%20missing%20women%20were%20untraced%2C%20as%20per%20NCRB%20figures%20for%202021%2C%20474%20minor%20girls%20and%202%2C711%20adult%20women%20remained%20untraced%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20those%20reported%20missing%20in%20previous%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaims%20of%20human%20trafficking%20aside%2C%20concerns%20over%20misuse%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20data%20gathered%20under%20e-governance%20initiatives%20aren%E2%80%99t%20new%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Such%20large-scale%20comprehensive%20collection%20of%20socio-economic%20data%20was%20first%20carried%20out%20in%20the%20state%20in%202016%2C%20under%20the%20previous%20TDP%20government%2C%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Smart%20Pulse%20Survey%20conducted%20state-wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurveyors%20carrying%20smartphones%20carried%20out%20an%20e-KYC%20(electronic%20Know%20Your%20Customer%2C%20a%20process%20by%20which%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20identity%20and%20address%20are%20verified%20digitally%20with%20Aadhaar%20authentication)%20targeting%20nearly%20socio-economic%20data%20of%201.48%20crore%20households%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20entries%20were%20also%20matched%20with%20the%20State%20Resident%20Data%20Hub%20(SRDH)%2C%20an%20Aadhaar-linked%20repository%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20data%2C%20to%20create%20%E2%80%98360-degree%20profiles%E2%80%99%20of%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClusters%20of%2050%20households%20were%20first%20created%20as%20part%20of%20this%20survey%2C%20and%20a%20similar%20mechanism%20is%20now%20used%20by%20village%20and%20ward%20volunteers%20too.%20Under%20the%20Smart%20Pulse%20Survey%2C%20officials%20used%20an%20app%20to%20collect%20various%20data%20points%20of%20residents%20to%20build%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98360-degree%20profile%E2%80%99%20database%20on%20residents%20in%20the%20name%20of%20ePragati%2C%20an%20authority%20which%20enables%20e-governance%20for%20providing%20citizen%20services%20and%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20village%20and%20ward%20volunteers%20are%20using%20various%20state%20government%20apps%2C%20including%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.ap.gsws.volunteer%5C%22%3EGrama%20Ward%20Sachivalayam%20Volunteer%20Mobile%20Application%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20gather%20citizens%E2%80%99%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20the%20kind%20of%20data%20inputs%20sought%20by%20each%20of%20these%20apps%2C%20based%20on%20the%20mobile%20app%20code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20code%20shows%20the%20parameters%20collected%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Smart%20Pulse%20Survey.%20The%20information%20sought%20in%20the%20app%20used%20for%20this%20survey%20includes%20the%20individual%E2%80%99s%20occupation%2C%20address%2C%20phone%20number%2C%20Aadhaar%20number%20(UID)%2C%20any%20agricultural%20vehicle%20owned%2C%20electricity%20bill%2C%20ration%20ID%2C%20their%20possessions%20including%20land%2C%20vehicle%2C%20refrigerator%20etc.%2C%20whether%20they%20hold%20any%20government%20job%2C%20whether%20they%20pay%20income%20tax%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20information%20became%20the%20foundation%20for%20deciding%20who%20should%20receive%20government%20welfare%20schemes.%20The%20information%20on%20income%20tax%20status%2C%20electricity%20consumption%2C%20land%20and%20vehicle%20ownership%2C%20having%20a%20government%20job%20etc.%20were%20used%20as%20the%20criteria%20for%20exclusion%20from%20government%20welfare%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20volunteer%20system%20is%20not%20just%20about%20welfare%20schemes.%20The%20data%20collected%20by%20village%20and%20ward%20volunteers%20is%20now%20used%20for%20day-to-day%20governance%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVolunteers%20have%20been%20roped%20in%20to%20carry%20out%20varied%20surveys%20related%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20education%2C%20health%2C%20livestock%20etc.%20usually%20carried%20out%20by%20individual%20departments%20for%20governance%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20volunteers%20use%20an%20app%20for%20these%20surveys%2C%20and%20code%20from%20the%20Grama%20Ward%20Sachivalayam%20Volunteer%20Mobile%20Application%20shows%20the%20kind%20of%20data%20they%20have%20been%20authorised%20to%20gather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%2050%20(or%20more)%20households%20allocated%20to%20the%20volunteer%20are%20listed%20on%20the%20app%2C%20with%20the%20volunteers%20expected%20to%20re-verify%20the%20household%20details%20once%20every%206%20months%20using%20Aadhaar%20e-KYC.%20Each%20household%20member%E2%80%99s%20information%20is%20collected%20with%20their%20name%2C%20household%20ID%2C%20Aadhaar%20number%20(UID)%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20mobile%20number%2C%20gender%20and%20door%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20code%20also%20shows%20that%20the%20volunteers%20can%20use%20the%20app%20to%20find%20out%20who%20is%20the%20head%20of%20the%20household%20and%20which%20family%20members%20are%20living%20in%20the%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20volunteers%20are%20also%20authorised%20to%20collect%20photos%20of%20the%20household%20members%2C%20geotagged%20with%20GPS%20location%20as%20part%20of%20these%20surveys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20volunteers%20are%20also%20able%20to%20gather%20details%20of%20citizens%E2%80%99%20religion%2C%20caste%20and%20even%20sub-caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20education%20survey%2C%20the%20volunteers%20were%20able%20to%20gather%20details%20of%20individuals%E2%80%99%20marital%20status%20along%20with%20other%20personal%20data%20already%20being%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20survey%20collected%20the%20following%20details%20of%20individuals%E2%80%99%20education%20and%20employment%20status%20%E2%80%93%20educational%20qualification%2C%20whether%20they%20know%20how%20to%20read%20and%20write%2C%20whether%20they%20have%20dropped%20out%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20their%20education%20and%20their%20reason%20for%20doing%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20the%20volunteers%20were%20the%20agents%20of%20last-mile%20governance%2C%20identifying%20people%E2%80%99s%20health%20status%2C%20distributing%20masks%20and%20even%20identifying%20the%20vaccination%20status%20of%20individuals.%20These%20are%20the%20health%20parameters%20volunteers%20were%20expected%20to%20collect%20using%20their%20app%20%E2%80%93%20including%20information%20on%20various%20non-communicable%20diseases%2C%20HIV%2FAIDS%20status%2C%20pregnancy%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20data%20is%20a%20lot%20more%20detailed%20than%20what%20was%20asked%20in%20the%20Union%20government%20apps%20designed%20for%20citizens%20%E2%80%93%20AarogyaSetu%20(for%20contact%20tracing%20and%20self-assessment)%20and%20CoWIN%20(for%20vaccination).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20June%2C%20a%20massive%20data%20breach%20came%20to%20light%20when%20the%20private%20information%20of%20lakhs%20of%20citizens%20who%20had%20used%20the%20CoWIN%20app%20to%20get%20their%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20was%20leaked%20by%20a%20Telegram%20bot.%20Delhi%20police%20have%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fco-win-data-leak-delhi-police-arrests-bihar-man%5C%22%3Earrested%20a%20man%20and%20his%20minor%20brother%20from%20Bihar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0over%20the%20data%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fcowin-data-leak-is-a-sign-india-needs-to-rethink-its-digital-public-infrastructure-strategy%5C%22%3ECoWIN%20Data%20Leak%20Is%20a%20Sign%20India%20Needs%20to%20Rethink%20its%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20Strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20these%20surveys%2C%20volunteers%20were%20also%20authorised%20to%20collect%20information%20related%20to%20regular%20welfare%20services%20including%20distribution%20of%20ration%2C%20pension%2C%20insurance%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20activities%20to%20promote%20livelihoods%20for%20people%20with%20livestock%2C%20the%20volunteer%20app%20lists%20code%20to%20collect%20information%20on%20dairy%20animals%20%E2%80%94%20a%20livestock%20census%20of%20sorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20also%20includes%20a%20questionnaire%20on%20local%20governance%2C%20on%20access%20to%20various%20civic%20services%20such%20as%20garbage%20collection%2C%20cleaning%20of%20roads%20and%20canals%2C%20water%20supply%2C%20functioning%20street%20lights%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20functions%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20app%2C%20which%20are%20primarily%20directed%20towards%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20schemes%20such%20as%20Amma%20Vodi%20(financial%20incentive%20for%20mothers%20of%20school-going%20children)%2C%20Manabadi%20Nadu%20Nedu%20(an%20infrastructure%20revamping%20scheme%20for%20schools)%2C%20YSR%20Nethanna%20Nestham%20(financial%20incentive%20to%20handloom%20weavers)%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20the%20app%20code%20suggests%20that%20the%20state%20government%20also%20collected%20information%20about%20the%20volunteers%20themselves%2C%20including%20the%20WhatsApp%20groups%20the%20volunteer%20is%20part%20of%20and%20whether%20the%20volunteer%20is%20reading%20a%20newspaper%20from%20the%20funds%20allocated%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20trying%20to%20put%20out%20the%20entire%20code%20here%2C%20but%20just%20enough%20to%20show%20the%20kind%20of%20information%20that%20is%20being%20collected%20from%20only%20one%20app%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Grama%20Ward%20Sachivalayam%20Volunteer%20Mobile%20Application%2C%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gswshelper.com%2F2021%2F09%2Fmobile-applications.html%5C%22%3Enumerous%20mobile%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0used%20by%20various%20government%20departments%20and%20even%20citizens%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20is%20collecting%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20data%20as%20part%20of%20their%20e-governance%20initiatives.%20Compared%20to%20a%20traditional%20census%20and%20survey%2C%20here%20the%20information%20is%20being%20collected%20continuously.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20lack%20of%20privacy%20that%20is%20guaranteed%20in%20anonymises%20census%20and%20statistical%20surveys%2C%20where%20only%20summarised%20data%20is%20shared%20with%20government%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20government%20departments%20have%20access%20to%20profiles%20of%20every%20individual%20with%20constant%20collection%20of%20personal%20data%20linked%20with%20their%20Aadhaar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20concern%20with%20such%20large-scale%20data%20collection%20is%20possible%20voter%20profiling%20%E2%80%93%20the%20fear%20that%20volunteers%20are%20possibly%20working%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20YSRCP%2C%20tracking%20the%20different%20needs%20of%20people%20to%20target%20them%20during%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202019%20Assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20TDP%20itself%20was%20accused%20of%20data%20theft.%20A%20private%20firm%20called%20IT%20Grids%20which%20had%20developed%20the%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20official%20app%20Seva%20Mitra%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fandhra-pradesh-stolen-aadhaar-data%5C%22%3Ewas%20booked%20for%20voter%20data%20theft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20allegedly%20stealing%20data%20related%20to%20Aadhaar%2C%20electoral%20rolls%20and%20beneficiaries%20of%20government%20schemes%20from%20the%20government%20database%20to%20help%20improve%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20election%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20first%20published%20in%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fhow-much-data-do-village-and-ward-volunteers-andhra-pradesh-collect-179900%5C%22%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0under%20Creative%20Commons%20Attribution%20%E2%80%93%20No%20Derivatives%204.0%20International%20(CC%20BY-ND%204.0)%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Read%20the%20original%20article%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fhow-much-data-do-village-and-ward-volunteers-andhra-pradesh-collect-179900%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa