%20and%20Mandi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20issued%20orange%20alerts%20for%20the%20Shimla%2C%20Solan%2C%20Sirmaur%2C%20Mandi%2C%20Bilaspur%2C%20Kangra%2C%20Chamba%2C%20Hamirpur%20and%20Una%20districts%20during%20the%20next%20three%20days.%20The%20rain%20will%20continue%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20If%20we%20see%20the%20records%20of%20the%20past%20100%20years%2C%20this%20year%20will%20be%20the%20highest%20rainfall%20year%20as%20it%20has%20broken%20all%20old%20records%20so%20far%20in%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Surender%20Paul%2C%20head%20of%20IMD%20(Shimla)%2C%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20been%20light%20rainfall%20during%20the%20past%2024%20hours%20in%20the%20state.%20There%20is%20a%20probability%20of%20landslides%20and%20fog%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20monsoon%20will%20continue%20till%20September.%20Monsoon%20so%20far%20there%20has%20been%20530%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20which%20is%20very%20high.%20We%20have%20received%20734%20mm%20of%20rain%20during%20the%20monsoon.%20We%20have%20received%2070%25%20prescription%20of%20the%20total%20rainfall.%20We%20have%20two%20more%20months%20of%20the%20monsoon%20season.%20We%20have%20issued%20an%20advisory%20and%20have%20also%20issued%20an%20orange%20alert%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Paul%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Revenue%20Minister%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20Jagat%20Singh%20Negi%20said%20that%20the%20alert%20is%20continued%20and%20all%20are%20prepared%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20heavy%20rain%20has%20destroyed%20roads%2C%20drinking%20and%20irrigation%20water%20supply%20schemes%20and%20there%20has%20been%20a%20loss%20of%20over%206000%20Crore%20rupees.%20188%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20194%20people%20are%20injured%20and%20a%20total%20of%20652%20houses%20have%20been%20damaged%20with%20nearly%206500%20houses%20damaged%20partially%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Negi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cloudbursts%20and%20