%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20office%20of%20California%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta.%20Investigators%20also%20found%20a%20stash%20of%20%26quot%3Billegally%20imported%20beverage%20containers%26quot%3B%20worth%20another%20%241%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20someone%20purchases%20a%20plastic%20or%20aluminum%20bottle%20in%20California%2C%20they%20typically%20pay%20an%20extra%205%20to%2010%20cents%20in%20%26quot%3BCalifornia%20Redemption%20Value%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20CRV%2C%20which%20the%20consumer%20can%20get%20back%20if%20they%20return%20the%20items%20to%20one%20of%20the%20state's%20more%20than%201%2C200%20recycling%20centers.%20Arizona%20has%20no%20such%20program.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalifornia's%20recycling%20program%20is%20funded%20by%20consumers%2C%20and%20helps%20protect%20our%20environment%20and%20our%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20Bonta%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20try%20to%20undermine%20its%20integrity%20through%20criminal%20operations%20will%20be%20held%20accountable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20criminal%20complaint%2C%20prosecutors%20specifically%20accuse%20the%20family%20members%20of%20unlawfully%20conspiring%20to%20commit%20grand%20theft%20and%2C%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bchronic%20and%20ongoing%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20defrauding%20the%20California%20recycling%20program%20by%20seeking%20reimbursement%20for%20out-of-state%20containers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20containers%20that%20had%20already%20been%20redeemed%20within%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFelony%20grand%20theft%20in%20California%20is%20punishable%20by%20up%20to%20three%20years%20in%20a%20state%20prison.%20Redeeming%20out-of-state%20containers%2C%20to%20the%20degree%20the%20family%20is%20accused%2C%20could%20also%20land%20the%20accused%20behind%20bars%20for%20another%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20documents%20did%20not%20identify%20an%20attorney%20for%20the%20defendants%2C%20who%20have%20not%20been%20convicted%20of%20a%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20six%20people%20were%20charged%20in%20a%20similar%20Arizona-to-California%20recycling%20scheme%20that%2C%20according%20to%20prosecutors%2C%20netted%20more%20than%20%2410%20million%20by%20fraudulently%20redeeming%20more%20than%20nine%20tons%20of%20empty%20beverage%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202010%20and%202019%2C%20at%20least%2093%20people%20in%20California%20were%20convicted%20of%20recycling%20fraud%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconsumerwatchdog.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2022-01%2FCASH%2520FOR%2520TRASH%25202022.pdf%5C%22%3Ea%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20nonprofit%20Consumer%20Watchdog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20news%20tip%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acdavis%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecdavis%40insider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-accused-of-recycling-fraud-after-collecting-76-million-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690409598000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c16b0f42834d00193e5798%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-accused-of-recycling-fraud-after-collecting-76-million-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20family%20members%20face%20years%20behind%20bars%20after%20prosecutors%20accused%20them%20of%20illegally%20importing%20178%20tons%20of%20cans%20and%20bottles%20from%20Arizona.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cdavis%40insider.com%20(Charles%20R.%20Davis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A194%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-accused-of-recycling-fraud-after-collecting-76-million-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deemed%20universities%20scrapping%20NRI%20quota%20for%20medical%20seats%22%2C%22content%22