E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20privilege.%20This%20was%20a%20blow%20to%20my%20privilege.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20an%20insult%20to%20me.%20My%20self-respect%20has%20been%20challenged.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20if%20the%20house%20is%20run%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20government%2C%20then%20I%20will%20understand%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20charged%2C%20even%20as%20Dhankhar%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnothing%20will%20go%20on%20record%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20DMK%20MP%20Tiruchi%20Siva%20also%20pointed%20out%20to%20Dhankhar%20that%20Kharge%20was%20repeatedly%20interrupted%20while%20he%20was%20speaking%20by%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20other%20members%20and%20was%20not%20able%20to%20convey%20what%20he%20wanted%20to%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20unprecedented%20manner%2C%20when%20the%20floor%20was%20given%20to%20him%20and%20he%20was%20speaking%2C%20his%20mike%20was%20switched%20off.%20This%20has%20never%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20that%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20mike%20has%20been%20switched%20off%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siva%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDhankhar%20then%20responded%20that%20he%20had%20received%20inputs%20from%20the%20deputy%20chairman%20and%20stated%20that%20no%20microphones%20were%20switched%20off.%20He%20added%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20that%20mikes%20were%20put%20off.%20If%20an%20honourable%20member%20transgresses%20to%20another%20issue%20that%20is%20not%20the%20subject%20of%20discussion%E2%80%A6%20That%20cannot%20be%20allowed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20also%20said%20that%20while%20media%20reports%20said%20that%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20been%20suspended%20for%20raising%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20it%20was%20not%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSuspension%20was%20not%20because%20he%20raised%20an%20issue.%20He%20was%20suspended%20for%20misconduct%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eputting%20it%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20that%20a%20member%20was%20suspended%20because%20of%20raising%20an%20issue%20is%20unpardonable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Monday%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-announces-nationwide-protest-against-sanjay-singhs-rajya-sabha-suspension-manipur-turmoil%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20was%20suspended%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Dhankhar%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20session%20for%20%E2%80%9Crepeatedly%20violating%20the%20directives%20of%20the%20chair%E2%80%9D%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20protested%20in%20parliament%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F07201357%2F2022_12img07_Dec_2022_PTI12_07_2022_000123B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F07201357%2F2022_12img07_Dec_2022_PTI12_07_2022_000123B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F07201357%2F2022_12img07_Dec_2022_PTI12_07_2022_000123B-300x158.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F07201357%2F2022_12img07_Dec_2022_PTI12_07_2022_000123B-1024x538.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-631798%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVice-president%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar.%20Photo%3A%20Sansad%20TV%20Screengrab%20via%20PTI%2FFile%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20when%20the%20house%20reconvened%20after%20lunch%2C%20Kharge%20announced%20that%20the%20opposition%20MPs%20will%20be%20staging%20a%20walkout%20as%20their%20demands%20are%20not%20being%20met%20and%20they%20are%20not%20even%20being%20allowed%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThank%20you%20for%20calling%20me%20to%20speak.%20I%20request%20you%20to%20not%20switch%20off%20my%20microphone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20discussion%20that%20we%20wanted%20in%20the%20house%2C%20we%20wanted%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20statement%20and%20are%20still%20waiting%20for%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20now%20it%20has%20been%20five%20days%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20not%20come.%20And%20he%20is%20watching%20everything%20from%20his%20office%20but%20not%20giving%20a%20statement.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20give%20a%20statement%20in%20front%20of%20him.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20is%20not%20giving%20us%20the%20chance%20to%20speak.%20This%20is%20why%20because%20of%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20government%20in%20protest%20we%20are%20walking%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20opposition%20was%20walking%20out%2C%20deputy%20chairman%20Harivansh%20Narayan%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20MPs%20must%20listen%20to%20what%20he%20had%20to%20say%20before%20leaving.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20house%20say%20that%20only%20the%20subject%20under%20consideration%20can%20be%20discussed.%20Today%2C%20a%20concern%20is%20being%20raised%20against%20these%20rules%20and%20procedures.%20Who%20are%20the%20people%20who%20made%20these%20rules%20and%20procedures%3F%20The%20country%20should%20ask%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhistory-no-confidence-motions-modi-government%5C%22%3EA%20Look%20at%20the%20History%20of%20No-Confidence%20Motions%2C%20as%20Modi%20Government%20Faces%20Its%20Second%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKharge%20writes%20to%20Shah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20Kharge%20also%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20saying%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20comparing%20the%20nomenclature%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%20to%20the%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20and%20East%20India%20Company%20is%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20single%20day%2C%20the%20respected%20Prime%20Minister%20connects%20the%20opposition%20parties%20of%20the%20country%20with%20the%20British%20rulers%20and%20the%20terrorist%20group%20and%20on%20the%20same%20day%20the%20Home%20Minister%20writes%20an%20emotional%20letter%20and%20expects%20a%20positive%20attitude%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20sharing%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20letter%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKharge%20was%20referring%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-shah-writes-manipur-opposition-mps-pm-statement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20letter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eto%20the%20leaders%20of%20opposition%20parties%20in%20both%20houses%20urging%20for%20cooperation%20for%20a%20discussion%20on%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20only%20absurd%20but%20also%20unfortunate%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20call%20the%20opposition%20parties%20directionless%20on%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20said%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20urging%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20come%20to%20the%20House%20and%20