0his%20objection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petitioner%2C%20his%20land%20measuring%20six%20kanal%20and%20two%20marlas%20at%20Mouza%20locality%20of%20Machail%20Paddar%20was%20forcibly%20taken%20over%20and%20the%20two%20companies%20started%20levelling%20the%20ground%20for%20constructing%20the%20helipad%2C%20allegedly%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20approached%20the%20administration%20for%20justice%20but%20instead%20of%20helping%20me%2C%20they%20sided%20with%20the%20two%20companies%20and%20started%20preparing%20the%20land%20for%20use%20as%20a%20helipad%20without%20my%20consent%20or%20paying%20any%20rent%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheikh%20Nasir%2C%20the%20counsel%20of%20Raj%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20quoting%20the%20petitioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasir%20said%20that%20despite%20being%20shown%20the%20cold%20shoulder%20by%20the%20administration%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20land%20continued%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20two%20companies%20repeatedly%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20months%20and%20requested%20them%20to%20vacate%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20companies%2C%20who%20seem%20to%20be%20well-connected%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20any%20heed%20to%20his%20requests.%20Even%20the%20administration%20officials%20advised%20him%20not%20to%20make%20this%20an%20issue%20as%20it%20was%20connected%20to%20a%20sacred%20pilgrimage%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nasir%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20petition%2C%20Raj%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20two%20companies%20again%20tried%20to%20level%20the%20land%20forcibly%20last%20week%20but%20they%20were%20stopped%20due%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctimely%20intervention%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20neighbours%20and%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20every%20apprehension%20that%20they%20(the%20administration%20and%20aviation%20companies)%20will%20forcibly%20trespass%20and%20make%20the%20use%20of%20suit%20land%2C%20hence%20the%20cause%20of%20action%20has%20accrued%20to%20the%20plaintiff%20in%20filing%20the%20present%20suit%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuling%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20land%20owner%2C%20the%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbalance%20of%20convenience%20tilts%20in%20favour%20of%20applicant%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20this%20stage%20if%20the%20interim%20injunction%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20not%20granted%2C%20there%20is%20every%20likelihood%20%5Bthat%20the%20land%20owner%20will%5D%20suffer%20irreparable%20loss%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20%5Bthe%20two%20companies%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20ruled%2C%20while%20asking%20the%20companies%20and%20the%20administration%20to%20vacate%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20Himalayan%20Heli%20Services%20Pvt%20Ltd%20and%20Aryan%20Aviation%20Pvt%20Ltd%20for%20their%20comment.%20This%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20their%20response%20is%20received.%20The%20divisional%20commissioner%20(Jammu)%20Ramesh%20Kumar%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20his%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20treacherous%20pilgrimage%20in%20Kishtwar%20to%20the%20high-altitude%20Himalayan%20shrine%20of%20Mata%20Chandi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20manifestations%20of%20Goddess%20Durga%2C%20is%20undertaken%20by%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20pilgrims%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2043-day%20pilgrimage%20started%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20arduous%2C%2030-km%20trek%20from%20Gulabgarh%20to%20Machail%20passes%20along%20the%20high%20mountains%20of%20Kishtwar%2C%20which%20are%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20finest%20and%20most-precious%20sapphires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20pilgrimages%20to%20Amarnath%20and%20Mata%20Vaishno%20Devi%20shrines%2C%20the%20Machail%20yatra%20is%20not%20managed%20by%20any%20independent%20board.%20The%20administration%20has%20set%20up%20the%20Machail%20Maata%20Yatra%20Management%20Committee%20which%20is%20headed%20by%20the%20divisional%20commissioner%20of%20Jammu%2C%20while%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Kishtwar%20is%20the%20vice-chairman%20of%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20official%20spokesperson%2C%20the%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%2C%20Jammu%2C%20Mukesh%20Singh%2C%20the%20deputy%20inspector%20general%20of%20Doda-Kishtwar-Ramban%20range%2C%20Sunil%20Gupta%2C%20and%20the%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20Kishtwar%20Devansh%20Yadav%20paid%20obeisance%20at%20the%20shrine%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM-300x192.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26195448%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-26-at-6.49.28-PM-1024x655.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665318%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22767%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EADGP%20Jammu%20Mukesh%20Singh%20and%20DC%20Kishtwar%20Devansh%20Yadav%20paid%20obeisance%20at%20the%20shrine%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20pilgrimage%20using%20the%20controversial%20helicopter%20service.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20all%20the%20senior%20officials%20visited%20the%20shrine%20by%20using%20the%20controversial%20helicopter%20service%2C%20which%20was%20introduced%20on%20th