3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCj7f9-Us0yV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Lori%20Mcfadyen%20(%40bakerycanadian)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20principal%2C%20management%2C%20and%20teacher%20aunty%20of%20the%20school%2C%20Lori%2C%20has%20taught%20hundreds%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERonit%20Rawat%2C%20a%20former%20student%20at%20the%20school%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20school%20from%20some%20friends%20who%20went%20there.%20If%20you%20visit%20Sainji%2C%20the%20hill%20right%20in%20front%20of%20it%20is%20my%20village%2C%20Kandital.%20The%20method%20of%20teaching%20in%20the%20school%20is%20quite%20different%20as%20it%20is%20very%20immersive%20and%20interactive.%20We%20had%20dance%20and%20painting%20classes.%20We%20would%20interact%20with%20people%20coming%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20to%20teach%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERonit%20is%20currently%20studying%20hotel%20management%20in%20Dehradun%20and%20is%20pursuing%20an%20internship%20with%20JW%20Marriott.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20student%20Mansi%20Bhandari%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20volunteering%20teacher%20at%20the%20school%20now%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20a%20library%2C%20a%20field%2C%20toilets%20etc%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20campus.%20While%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F121081%2Fmumbai-professor-sandeep-desai-shloka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnglish%20medium%20schools%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Mussoorie%2C%20the%20fee%20is%20enormous%20and%20we%20cannot%20afford%20it.%20The%20school%20and%20Lori%20Aunty%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20blessing%20for%20me%20and%20many%20children%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20education%20here%20is%20as%20good%20as%20any%20private%20school%2C%20and%20we%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20dream%20big%20and%20get%20jobs%20in%20cities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansi%20is%20currently%20pursuing%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20arts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20her%20journey%20so%20far%2C%20Lori%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20my%20teacher%20in%20anthropology%20would%20always%20say%20how%20I%20should%20be%20running%20an%20NGO%20instead%20of%20becoming%20a%20professor.%20As%20we%20can%20see%2C%20he%20was%20right.%20The%20path%20my%20life%20took%20is%20so%20much%20more%20fulfilling%20and%20worthwhile%20than%20being%20only%20a%20teacher.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESponsorships%2C%20volunteering%2C%20and%20how%20you%20can%20help!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20charge%20a%20very%20minimal%20fee%20of%20Rs%20200%20to%20the%20children%2C%20with%20books%20and%20uniforms%2C%20the%20burden%20can%20be%20a%20lot%20for%20some%20parents.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20run%20a%20sponsorship%20programme%20for%20the%20children%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20program%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20programme%2C%20we%20sponsor%20students%20who%20need%20the%20most%20help.%20Sponsors%20contribute%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20month%2C%20which%20covers%20all%20expenses%2C%20including%20transportation%20(if%20needed)%2C%20books%2C%20and%20uniforms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1-1690374011.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kids%20from%20the%20Garhwal%20school.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fschool-1-1690374011.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F