oseph%20Nzuamkende%20Mwendo%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20trek%2C%20we%20always%20advise%20everyone%20to%20walk%20%3Cem%3Epolley%20polley%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20means%20walking%20slowly.%20We%20take%20small%20steps%2C%20sing%2C%20and%20chat%20to%20make%20the%20journey%20easier.%20Aadya%20was%20the%20youngest%20person%20I%E2%80%99ve%20ever%20trekked%20with%2C%20but%20she%20completed%20it%20just%20like%20any%20other%20adult.%20She%20showed%20remarkable%20patience%20even%20when%20she%20was%20in%20pain.%20I%20was%20amazed%20to%20see%20her%20determination%20and%20strength.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-3-1690378273.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aadya%20with%20her%20guides%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-3-1690378273.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-3-1690378273-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-3-1690378273-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-3-1690378273-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faadya-bennur-3-1690378273-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325237%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAadya%20says%20imagining%20herself%20holding%20the%20Indian%20flag%20on%20the%20peak%20motivated%20her%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Harsha%20Bennur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20completed%20the%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20trek%20successfully%20with%20Aadya%2C%20Harsha%20is%20still%20not%20able%20to%20get%20over%20the%20rea