h%20EkStep%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20late%201800s%2C%20when%20Dr%20Maria%20Montessori%20was%20working%20at%20a%20psychiatric%20clinic%20in%20Rome%2C%20she%20would%20often%20visit%20asylums%20for%20children%20with%20intellectual%20disabilities%20(then%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmental%20disorders%E2%80%9D).%20It%20was%20here%20that%20she%20observed%20that%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324494%2Fplaygrounds-for-children-in-india-learning-early-childhood-growth-education-anthill-creations%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20needed%20a%20more%20stimulating%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20such%20a%20bare%2C%20unfurnished%20room%2C%20%5Bthey%5D%20were%20desperate%20for%E2%80%A6activities%20for%20their%20hands%2C%20and%20that%20this%20deprivation%20was%20contributing%20to%20their%20condition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20observation%20was%20among%20the%20first%20seeds%20sowed%20for%20what%20is%20now%20known%20as%20the%20Montessori%20method%2C%20which%2C%20over%20a%20century%20later%2C%20has%20spread%20far%20and%20wide%20across%20the%20world%20and%20to%20children%20across%20the%20spectrum.%20It%20encourages%20a%20%E2%80%98different%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98informal%E2%80%99%20way%20of%20learning.%20Though%20acknowledged%20to%20have%20both%20pros%20and%20cons%2C%20Dr%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20pioneered%20early%20childhood%20education%20in%20a%20way%20that%20helps%20children%20develop%20their%20own%20pace%20and%20learning%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20820px)%20100vw%2C%20820px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Maria%20Montessori%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet