ying.%20I%20never%20imagined%20that%20I%20would%20get%20the%20first%20rank%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20result%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20seven%20years%20of%20hard%20work%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20by%20Sunil%20but%20by%20his%20family%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20of%20determination%20and%20sacrifice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sunil%20being%20felicitated%20by%20a%20police%20officer%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsunil4-1689688250-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324266%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunil%20being%20felicitated%20by%20a%20police%20officer%20in%20his%20village%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20village%20called%20Ranjit%20Nagar%20in%20Washim%2C%20Maharashtra.%20Second%20among%20five%20children%2C%20he%20faced%20many%20hardships%20growing%20up.%20Their%20parents%20would%20toil%20on%20the%20farm%20all%20day%20to%20ensure%20a%20good%20future%20for%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20about%20five%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20the%20Vidarbha%20region%2C%20which%20is%20dry.%20For%20most%20years%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20spent%20more%20on%20cultivation%20than%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20earned%20as%20income.%20But%20my%20parents%20always%20supported%20my%20ambition%20and%20worked%20on%20road%20construction%20to%20help%20me%20succeed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20studied%20till%20Class%2012%20in%20his%20village%20and%20completed%20his%20BA%20through%20an%20open%20university.%20Hailing%20from%20a%20small%20community%20called%20Mathura%20Labhan%2C%20he%20says%20he%20always%20aspired%20to%20become%20a%20policeman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20seeing%20everyone%20in%20my%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277209%2Fganjam-collector-vijay-amruta-kulange-inspiring-ias-officer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20village%20struggling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20always%20in%20a%20hand-to-mouth%20situation.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20interest%20in%20farming%20and%20saw%20how%20difficult%20it%20was.%20When%20we%20headed%20out%2C%20I%20always%20found%20the%20policemen%20fascinating.%20The%20way%20they%20walked%20and%20talked%2C%20their%20energy%20was%20different.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20like%20them%20ever%20since%20I%20was%20a%20child.%20And%20I%20thought%20it%20would%20also%20help%20improve%20our%20social%20status%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20Sunil%20continued%20working%20on%20the%20farm%20and%20did%20odd%20jobs%20to%20help%20his%20family%20till%20he%20completed%20his%20graduation.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Sambhaji%20Nagar%2C%20Aurangabad%2C%20to%20fulfil%20his%20dream%20of%20becoming%20a%20sub-inspector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESambhaji%20Nagar%20was%20one%20of%20the%20hubs%20for%20MPSC%20coaching%2C%20but%20Sunil%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20the%20classes.%20So%20he%20studied%20with%20his%20friends%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3